			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Just to get everyone up to date on this Quest...the hay is found on the Millers Farm in West Karana. Most of the Miller's will drop it just when walking around. You CAN kill the Gnoll Miller and he sometimes has the hay though. The Blessed Oil can be found by talking to a person in the Temple of Life. I have yet to get my hay cursed by the priest of Cazic-Thule. <BR>
<BR>
Because the Blessed Oil is &quot;NO DROP&quot;, you must be somewhat skilled in blacksmithing to complete the quest. <BR>
<BR>
BTW, does anyone know the stats on the Wee Harvester and Riverer Belt?
